name: Why So Serious?: The Mixtape
description:
Coming Winter 2008

Starting as a pet project in Summer 2008 after being inspired by anarchic psychopath 'The Joker' in 'The Dark Knight' feature film, O4TS attempts to capture the psychotic nature in lyrics and music, as well as relying on samples taken directly from the movie itself.

Track Listing:
1. Good Evening
2. War Paint
3. A Better Class
4. The Message
5. Chaos Ensues
6. The Joker

name: The Prelude
description:
Coming Winter 2008

The first release from hip-hop artist O4TS, 'The Prelude' is simply a showcase of talent, skill, and emotions taken from everyday life.

Track Listing:
1. Intro
2. Never Planned On It
3. Iller Than Me (Interlude)
4. Mind State
5. Flawless
6. Brutal
7. Sealed Fate
8. Vengeance
9. Rebellion (Interlude)
10. Subterfuge
11. The Journey (Part I of III)
12. All I Want
13. Photogenic
14. Outro
15. Stalingrad (Bonus)

name: Brick & Mortar Vol. 1: Destroy
description:
Coming Spring 2009

The first official mixtape from hip-hop artist O4TS shows the lyrical consistency in this young, unnoticed, up-and-coming MC. Following a similar vein to 'The Prelude', O4TS aims to appease hip-hop heads and test the listener's emotional ranges through a variety of songs.

Track Listing:
1. Reconsideration 
2. State Of The Game 
3. Realest 
4. Garbage Day 
5. Slow Defeat 
6. The Build-Up 
7. Ease Your Mind 
8. Liquor Store Blues 
9. Total Annihilation 
10. Mechanical 
11. If I Had (Remix) 
12. The Grim Reaper 
13. Less Of A Chance 
14. Don't Know 
15. Superhero
